subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Tony Eury Jr. spent the last six weeks on suspension after Nascar discovered unapproved brackets on the rear wing of Earnhardt’s Car of Tomorrow at Darlington.
